msgstr "[Connexions HTTPS per defecte](https://gitlab.com/fdroid/fdroidclient/blob/v0.100.1/app/src/main/res/values/default_repo.xml#L11)"

#. type: Bullet: '-   '
#: _docs/Security_Model.md
