msgid "Production signing is handled by [reproducible builds](https://tests.reproducible-builds.org/debian/rb-pkg/unstable/amd64/android-platform-tools-apksig.html) of _apksigner_ from Debian."
msgstr "La signatura de producció es gestiona amb [construccions reproduïbles](https://tests.reproducible-builds.org/debian/rb-pkg/unstable/amd64/android-platform-tools-apksig.html) de _apksigner_ de Debian."

