msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _docs/Take-Down_Requests.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<!--\n"
"  this is very loosely inspired by:\n"
"    * https://docs.github.com/en/github/site-policy/submitting-content-removal-requests\n"
